<!DOCTYPE lang="en">

<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/weather.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="main-content">
        {{>navbar}}
        <div class="contact-jean">
            <p>
                Jean Niho is still learning and pretty much like challenges and feedbacks/suggestions from others to improve his skills.
                Please provide a feedback on this working project, whether it be a comment, complain, suggestion, whatever it is you want to say
                you are more than welcome to express yourself. And please note that your response under this section will remain anonymous.
            </p>
            <h4 class="contact-form-heading">
                You can contact Jean Niho directly via the about section for private conversion/s.
            </h4>
            <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xleolqaw" method="post" id="contact-form" class="contact-form">
                <div class="contact-form-content">
                    <div class="input-field contact-message">
                        <textarea name="message " id="message " cols="30 " rows="7" type="text " class="contact-textarea" placeholder="Leave a message..." required></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="contact-btn" type="submit " value="Send ">Send</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    {{>footer}}
</body>

</html>